				<td><img src="/skins/default/images/user_IsOffline.gif" alt="Savidge is not online. Last active: 11/9/2004 3:39:22 PM" border="0" />&nbsp;<a class="SmallBoldText" href="/User/UserProfile.aspx?UserName=Savidge">Savidge</a><br></td>
